  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Reduction of the duration of vaso occlusive crisis (VOC) in subjects with sickle cell disease.</measure>
    <time_frame>Study participants will be followed for the duration of hospital stay, an expected average of 4 days</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
